Feature Space Training for Anomalous Sound Detection in Unlabeled Conditions\n     https://arxiv.org/abs/2409.09332\n     [authors=Takuya Fujimura, Ibuki Kuroyanagi, Tomoki Toda | published=2024-09-14 | primary_category=eess.AS | id=2409.09332]\n  4. Improving Anomalous Sound Detection through Pseudo-anomalous Set Selection and Pseudo-label Utilization under Unlabeled Conditions\n     https://arxiv.org/abs/2505.18980\n     [authors=Ibuki Kuroyanagi, Takuya Fujimura, Kazuya Takeda, Tomoki Toda | published=2025-05-25 | primary_category=cs.SD | id=2505.18980]\n  5. Performance improvement of spatial semantic segmentation with enriched audio features and agent-based error correction for DCASE 2025 Challenge Task 4\n     https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.21174\n     [authors=Jongyeon Park, Joonhee Lee, Do-Hyeon Lim, Hong Kook Kim, Hyeongcheol Geum, Jeong Eun Lim | published=2025-06-26 | primary_category=eess.AS | id=2506.21174]\n\n=== openalex (4 results) ===\n  1. Training-Free Model Selection and Domain-Aware Score Calibration for First-Shot Anomalous Sound Detection\n     https://openalex.org/W7167748121\n     [rank=1 | id=W7167748121]\n  2. Sub-Band Spectral Matching with Localized Score Aggregation for Robust Anomalous Sound Detection\n     https://openalex.org/W7139144037\n     [rank=2 | id=W7139144037]\n  3. Dynamic Training Strategies for Domain Generalization in Self-Supervised Anomaly Sound Detection\n     https://openalex.org/W7164852436\n     [rank=3 | id=W7164852436]\n  4. 実環境下におけるデータの取得制約を考慮した異常音検知\n     https://openalex.org/W7162976310\n     [rank=4 | id=W7162976310]\n\n=== openreview (5 results) ===\n  1. Robust Prototype Learning for Anomalous Sound Detection\n     https://openreview.net/forum?id=P55mVThDtO\n     [authors=Xiao-Min Zeng, Yan Song, Ian McLoughlin, Lin Liu, Li-Rong Dai | rank=1 | id=P55mVThDtO]\n  2. Self-Discriminative Modeling for Anomalous Graph Detection\n     https://openreview.net/forum?id=l9DJGAtoAj\n     [authors=Jinyu Cai, Yunhe Zhang, Ji